  "body": "![Cosmicore Logo](https://github.com/Starexify/Cosmicore/blob/1.21-neo/src/main/resources/cosmicore_logo.png?raw=true)\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n        <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/cosmicore\">\n          <img alt=\"curseforge\" height=\"56\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/available/curseforge_vector.svg\">\n        </a>\n        <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/cosmicore\">\n          <img alt=\"modrinth\" height=\"56\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/available/modrinth_vector.svg\">\n        </a>\n</p>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n        <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/cosmicore\">\n          <img alt=\"CurseForge Downloads\" src=\"https://img.shields.io/curseforge/dt/1057420?style=for-the-badge&logo=curseforge&color=1B3193\">\n        </a>\n        <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/cosmicore\">\n          <img alt=\"Modrinth Downloads\" src=\"https://img.shields.io/modrinth/dt/I6sYca4V?style=for-the-badge&logo=modrinth&color=1B3193\">\n        </a>\n</p>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n        <a href=\"https://x.com/FoxiStar9\"><img alt=\"X (formerly Twitter) URL\" src=\"https://img.shields.io/twitter/url?url=https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FFoxiStar9&style=for-the-badge&logo=x&logoColor=000000&label=Follow%20Us&color=555555\">\n        </a>\n        <a href=\"https://github.com/Starexify/Cosmicore/issues\">\n          <img alt=\"GitHub Issues\" src=\"https://img.shields.io/github/issues/Starexify/Cosmicore?style=for-the-badge&color=1B3193\">\n        </a>\n        <a href=\"https://github.com/Starexify/Cosmicore/blob/1.21/LICENSE\">\n          <img alt=\"GitHub License\" src=\"https://img.shields.io/github/license/Starexify/Cosmicore?style=for-the-badge&color=1B3193\">\n        </a>\n</p>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n    <a href=\"https://starexify.github.io/FnB-Projects/src/\"><img alt=\"F&B Projects Hub\" height=\"56\" src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Starexify/Starexify/b79e6e8e9e0772de98a4584e41476894a655ac0c/resources/Minecraft/Desc/site/cozy_vector.svg\"></a>\n</p>\n\n&nbsp;\n\n## ℹ️ About\n\nCosmicore is a brand-new meteors mod for minecraft, inspired by the nostalgia of the old Falling Meteors mod, but with more content.\n\n## ✨ Features\n\n<table align=\"center\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse;\">\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td style=\"padding: 10px; text-align: left; border: none;\"><strong>🏛️ Structures</strong></td>\n      <td style=\"padding: 10px; text-align: left; border: none;\">Six <strong>Fallen Meteor Sites</strong> where you can find the new meteors and <em>lore</em>.</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td style=\"padding: 10px; text-align: left; border: none;\"><strong>🪨 New Materials</strong></td>\n      <td style=\"padding: 10px; text-align: left; border: none;\"><strong>Titanium</strong>, <strong>Lonsdaleite</strong>, <strong>Infernium</strong> and <strong>Magnetite</strong> are the new materials.</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td style=\"padding: 10px; text-align: left; border: none;\"><strong>⚙️ Machines</strong></td>\n      <td style=\"padding: 10px; text-align: left; border: none;\"><strong>Two New Crushing Machines</strong> are added to crush the meteors to a crust.</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td style=\"padding: 10px; text-align: left; border: none;\"><strong>☄️ METEORS!!</strong></td>\n      <td style=\"padding: 10px; text-align: left; border: none;\">Three new types of meteors: <strong>Achondrite</strong>, <strong>Meteorite</strong>, and <strong>Pallasite</strong>.</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n## 🗓️ Planned Updates\n\nIn the upcoming updates we plan to add:\n\n- ☄️ **MORE METEORS!!**\n- Even more structures\n- Even more materials\n- More new machines\n- And more!\n\n## 📜 License\n\nThis mod is licensed under the MIT License, allowing for free use, modification, and distribution, meaning you can use\nour mod in your modpacks. For more details, please see the full license included with the mod.\n",
